Scenario: The application is called with no command line arguments and no valid configuration file
    Given a test environment with no config
    When we call the application without command line arguments
    Then the call should fail with return code  1
    And stderr must contain  Could not find a settings file

Scenario: The application is called with no command line arguments and a valid configuration file
    Given a test environment with a valid config
    When we call the application without command line arguments
    Then the call should fail with return code  1
    And stderr must contain  must define at least one command
